{"tid":240924,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"［求救］下星期二去台灣 特區護照離到期日不足六個月","createTime":"2017-05-12T18:30:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-13T06:22:21.000Z","uid":19874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"01b42e92d70138ab8ad603850c4148740d39c208","tid":240924,"uid":19874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T18:30:59.000Z","msg":"小弟下星期二飛台灣旅行 機票酒店咩都訂好哂 但發現特區護照距離到期日唔夠六個月<br />\n今日臨急臨忙上網search 最後見到好似BNO可以做快證 最快兩小時就拎到 跟住我就約左星期一去英國領事館辦理<br />\n<br />\n想問幾個問題....<br />\n<br />\n1.我本BNO過期未超過十年 整到緊急快證既機會大唔大 有冇咩要注意？<br />\n<br />\n2.萬一唔得...我特區護照係10月22到期 仲有冇任何機會入到台灣？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我好擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caf98785d46b3c4b6242cf649347e1bf8d5861eb","tid":240924,"uid":42411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T18:35:23.000Z","msg":"BNO未過10年<br />\n可book星期一去英國領事館整<br />\n記得print埋電子機票<br />\n帶錢（可以credit card/EPS/cash）相/填好嘅form<br />\n一個鐘頭就拎得<br />\n<br />\n利由 上年整過"},{"pid":"43df61dd7822334365567a29f7abb0d4932ad6a1","tid":240924,"uid":19874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T18:39:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>BNO未過10年<br />\n可book星期一去英國領事館整<br />\n記得print埋電子機票<br />\n帶錢（可以credit card/EPS/cash）相/填好嘅form<br />\n一個鐘頭就拎得<br />\n<br />\n利由 上年整過</blockquote><br />\n我已經book左星期一去<br />\n張form係邊到down<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我以為係去到先填 好在問一問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" clas